data.description: Home Sweet Oklahoma! Escape to the quiet country life and relax under the stars on your front deck. Plenty of room for horses, boats and all the big toys. Spacious split floor plan, new windows, and 5.5 acres of flat open land for growing and building. Lots of wildlife and very secluded. Master suite could be office or nursery.
